selection operators
m       Match
v       inVert selection
n       select by Number
u       select Unique

translation operators
s       Substitution
y       transliteration

operators
d       sunDer selected
cs      Coalesce
x       eXchange

operators
r       Reverse
ss      Sort Strings (asc)
sn      Sort Numeric (asc)

filesystem operators
ls      directory LiSting
rp      path canonicalization (with RealPath)
stat		stat each path, printf(fmt) with results (like find printf)

/* (-f) path references a plain file */
/* (-d) path references a directory */
/* (-l) path references a symbolic link */
